Subject: [PATCH] apparmor: Fix string overrun due to missing termination
References: bsc#1012628 CVE-2026-46055 bsc#1266682
Patch-mainline: 7.0.4
Git-commit: 828bf7929bedcb79b560b5b4e44f22abee07d31b

commit 828bf7929bedcb79b560b5b4e44f22abee07d31b upstream.

